title: Share of Americans with at least one tattoo - by age 2003 to 2015
summary: This grouped bar chart shows SOME LABEL on the Y-axis for 6 different Countrys for 4 groups 2003, 2008, 2012, and 2015 that are presented on the X-axis.
In Country 30 to 39, 2015 had the highest SOME LABEL 55.0 among the 4 groups and in 65 and older, 2012 had the lowest SOME LABEL 5.0.
Among all the Countrys, 2015 had the highest SOME LABEL in Country 30 to 39 and lowest SOME LABEL in Country 65 and older.
There is a gap of 44.0 between the highest and lowest SOME LABEL found for 2015 in Country 30 to 39 and 65 and older.
